body_text:
b'This is a 2 bedroom 2bath apartment unit in a gated, clean and quiet community with 2 swimming pools, one fitting room, close to 880 and New Park Mall. 

 I'm looking for a no smoking, no drug, no alcohol roommate. 

 You have:
 1) Private bedroom(12"x11.3") furnished with one single bed, one desk, two book shelves, wall to wall closet; 
 2) Private bathroom with shower over tub;
 3) The rent includes PGE, water, garbage, wifi, parking inside the community; 
 4) You share the kitchen and living room with one person only;
 5) Good references and credit check may required;

If you are interested, or have any questions, please email me, or ring me up.'
